column5: heading up in 2 weeks anyone want to talk?

Swanee, We'll be there in two weeks as well. Hard to focus at work lately... I'm trying to temper my expectations as last year I landed my PB pike at 45". That'll be tough to beat. I guess I still have that 30" walleye to get. Good luck on your trip!
I won't be there for a couple of months, so I will say I am very jealous of you.Have a safe and wonderful trip.....
1850 lund tyee we beach on the back bay look us up
